{"tid":1737743,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] Pokémon 劍盾討論區 #19 不推文回覆 光復香港","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T00:25:01.000Z","uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aa23a986a7ab2968267143877952e743c81e7fcf","tid":1737743,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/04/yR9KpW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F04%2FyR9KpW.png&h=61d6ecb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此POST並非小圈子<br />\n<br />\n禁止討論修改及盜版遊戲<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請支持官方授權<br />\n<br />\n香港Pok&eacute;mon比賽</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://playpokemonhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaypokemonhk.com%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2a5254d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://playpokemonhk.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPlayPokemonHK%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=b0c6f3d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efac1bfd2d83bc4c3a86c867f8c64776ec55e80","tid":1737743,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Q&amp;A</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 我買日版遊戲會唔會有中文？</strong><br />\n買咩版都有齊九國語言 記住冇得中途改<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 點解刷極都係女比卡超/伊貝既？我想要仔</strong><br />\n性別係開game一刻就鎖定左 要刷就要由頭玩過<br />\n性格就可以係草前面save再刷<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 咁點樣刪save？</strong><br />\n入Switch setting搞<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 比卡超、伊貝同夢夢咩性格好？</strong><br />\n比卡超：只玩特攻-timid 雙刀-naive/hasty<br />\n伊貝： 暫時推介adamant (玩專用技可考慮Modest, 只對人戰亦可考慮加防/特防性格)<br />\n夢夢： 好多性格都得 但做攻手唔夠超夢夢/富迪爭 刷Bold當盾都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n性格表google下就會有 *如果過關爆機就棄game的話其實冇必要刷*<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 咩係連鎖？</strong><br />\n淨係撞同一隻，狂捉<br />\n中間唔可以遇其他寵<br />\n如果遇左其他寵走佬就得<br />\n即係連續30場捉同一隻全部捉晒<br />\n30連後有機會出6V 同提高出色違機率<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6. 邊度Check 6V? 咩係6V？</strong><br />\nCheck V 地點: 11號道路通道上層博士<br />\nV係指單項個體值最高(31), 6V就係6項個體值皆最高<br />\n留意6V唔代表最完美 特攻型精靈應該刷5V 0攻<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7. 粒波點熄聲？</strong><br />\n中間粒制同頂制 兩個制一齊禁<br />\n入左精靈之後，長按粒的，之後變左精靈隻色再即刻按頂果粒制，會即刻震，就ok<br />\n可能要拎左夢夢先熄得聲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>8. 皮卡丘伊布胡地快龍拉普拉斯超夢我想知呢...</strong><br />\n冇人識你依堆咩黎 想討論唔該用返港式譯名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>參考網站(USUM資訊)</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n培育入門<span style=\"color: red;\">(新手必睇)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftut1.hkgpkm.pw&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=3d5d6817\" target=\"_blank\">http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\n傷害計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemon-trainer.net%2Fsm%2Fdmcs%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=42ef24b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemonshowdown.com%2Fdamagecalc%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=ada4e850\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n個體計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serebii.net%2Fgames%2Fiv-calcsm.shtml&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e491513c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最大耐久指數計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpkc.client.jp%2Fw%2Fdefmax.html&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=a5ae091f\" target=\"_blank\">http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n圖鑑/資料網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserebii.net%2Fpokedex-sm%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bb4b3300\" target=\"_blank\">http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbokevon.web.fc2.com%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=c2564a57\" target=\"_blank\">http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/</a> (英日中)"},{"pid":"e81e20b73f6e735a432dfbde6bfa72812b918819","tid":1737743,"uid":47898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"有無人派水主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733ca6895b57583ab1ca3571e6fdcaa45652e036","tid":1737743,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"3aea84166d1709079371ceae69bbdf8f3aa999a2","tid":1737743,"uid":185893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"隻盾係咪應該刷+A -SA"},{"pid":"aae4b153c1476c6dc88247f0eed29114fa91bbd6","tid":1737743,"uid":125160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"想問下毒龍 無極汰那 有冇必要刷5v?<br />\n爆機後，係未可以食野變做6v? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a18be8519d185d3c4816070ee28ec2f0317ecd","tid":1737743,"uid":4462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11